title: Eddie Redmayne's red carpet nerves (Bang Showbiz)
text: He has a reputation as of the hardest workers in the music biz, but the last year of Ronan Keating’s career has undoubtedly been on of the the most action-packed. 44 minutes ago One Direction’s Louis Tomlinson has poked fun at a supposed rift between him and bandmate Liam Payne, after the pair were caught in an apparent punch up on stage.
